***  Calculator - CS2006 Haskell 1  ***
---------------------------------------

To run the program:
-------------------

  1. unpack the files from the zip
  2. navigate to the main directory
  3. build the project using cabal:
	$ cabal configure
	$ cabal build
  4. Run the executable:
        $ ./dist/build/calculator/calculator


To read the documentation:
--------------------------

  1. Generate the documentation:
	$ cabal haddock --executables
  2. Navigate to:
	$ dist/doc/html/calculator/calculator
  3. Open html pages


After usage:
------------

  1. Clean up the program:
	$ cabal clean
